Package: python-cloudflare
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: python-cloudflare-doc
Description: Python wrapper for the Cloudflare API v4 (Python 2)
 python-cloudflare is a Python wrapper providing full access to the CloudFlare
 v4 API.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 2.

