Package: cli4
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-cloudflare (= ${source:Version})
Description: Command line frontend to the Cloudflare API v4 (Python 3)
 cli4 is a command line frontend to python-cloudflare, providing full access
 to the CloudFlare v4 API.
 .
 This package installs cli4 using Python 3 libraries.

